Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:20.42,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Don't wanna.}Không thích.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:22.78,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Man, you're kinda annoying.}Cái thái độ gì thế?
