Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:34.31,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Kumogakure, actually.}Kumogakure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:38.28,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Kumogakure? Never met someone \Nwith that name before.}Kumogakure? Cái tên hiếm có ghê.
