Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.79,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{What? It is?!}Hả? Thật á?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:49.17,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{It's common knowledge. Ask anyone.}Cái đó ai chả biết. Hỏi thử đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:51.17,Flashback,Homeroom Teach,0,0,0,,{Oh, come on, now...}Này này...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:53.67,Flashback,Homeroom Teach,0,0,0,,{You can't just lie about stuff like that.}Em không nên nói dối chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:57.32,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{It was a lie?! That is so annoying!}Nói dối hả? Bực quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.17,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Wait, it was a lie?}Hả? Nói dối ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.30,Flashback,Homeroom Teach,0,0,0,,{You're asking me?}Sao lại hỏi tôi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:04.81,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Noguchi, the teacher says not to lie.}Noguchi, thầy nói không nên nói dối.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:07.53,Flashback,Homeroom Teach,0,0,0,,{I was telling you that, actually.}Ừ, tôi nói em đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:11.52,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Can we drop this subject? \NI'm getting confused.}Chúng ta bỏ qua câu chuyện này được không?
