Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:16.60,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I'll go back and add enough mistakes \Nto make it seem natural.}Sau đó làm cho nó sai thật tự nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.61,FlashbackTop,Homeroom Teacher,0,0,0,,{The samurai class at the time \Nrebelled against this,}Tầng lớp samurai lại tiếp tục đứng lên,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:20.83,FlashbackTop,Homeroom Teacher,0,0,0,,{and that became known as the Nakasendai War.}và nó trở thành trận chiến Nakasendai
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:23.20,FlashbackTop,Homeroom Teacher,0,0,0,,{Then...}Sau đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.55,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Ew! Ew!}Gớm quá! Gớm quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.21,Flashback,Homeroom Teacher,0,0,0,,{What is it, Noguchi?}Gì thế Noguchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.60,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Bugs! Everywhere!}Bọ! Bọ ở khắp nơi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:33.79,Flashback,Homeroom Teach,0,0,0,,{Are those eggs or something?}Trứng con gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:37.87,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{There are so many and they're \Ndifferent colors and it's nasty!}Nó có nhiều màu sắc và gớm quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:42.36,Flashback,Homeroom Teach,0,0,0,,Tôi nghĩ là gạo... không phải trứng...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:46.57,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Oh, those things will give \Nyou the nastiest rash.}Sờ vào sẽ bị phát ban đó thầy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:50.71,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{The Japanese name for them is "Pseudo-Rice."}Ở Nhật gọi nó là "Gạo giả"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:54.04,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Pretty rare, actually, \Nand their eggs are crazy toxic.}Nó khá là hiếm và trứng của nó rất độc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:57.46,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{They're set up like that, two at a time,}Nó hay có hình dạng 2 trứng dính nhau\N và xếp thành hàng,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:08:00.83,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{so that right after birth, \Nthe male and female pairs}sau khi sinh ra sẽ là một cặp đực cái
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:03.15,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{can start reproducing immediately.}và tiếp tục sinh sản.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:07.01,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{That's somehow even worse!}Gớm quá đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:10.14,Flashback,Homeroom Teach,0,0,0,,{D-Do bugs like that really exist?}C-có loại bọ đó hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:11.99,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{It's a big world, you know.}Thế giới rộng lớn lắm thầy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:15.17,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Much bigger than what we cover in class.}Lớn hơn những gì chúng ta tưởng tượng...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:18.49,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{There are all kinds of bugs like that, \Nwhich may or may not exist.}Có những loại bọ chúng ta\N tưởng chúng không tồn tại.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:21.44,Flashback,Homeroom Teach,0,0,0,,{Well, better safe than sorry.}Mà thôi, an toàn là trên hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:22.90,Flashback,Homeroom Teach,0,0,0,,{Noguchi, grab a broom.}Noguchi, mang chổi ra đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:24.90,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Roger that!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:37.22,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Oh, my eraser fell.}A, tẩy rơi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:39.16,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Let's see...}Xem nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:54.96,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Somebody touched my ass!}Có ai đó chạm vào mông em!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:59.94,Flashback,Homeroom Teach,0,0,0,,{Settle down, Noguchi! There's no one \Nclose enough to you to have done that!}Noguchi, bình tĩnh lại! Làm gì có ai gần em!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:04.19,DefaultTop,Homeroom Teach,0,0,0,,{Easy now, Noguchi! Deep breaths! Come on!}Nào Noguchi! Thở từ từ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:03.71,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{That'll buy me a few seconds. \NLet's fill in the Japanese answers first...}Sẽ câu giúp mình ít thời gian! \NGiờ thì điền đáp án nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:07.76,Flashback,Homeroom Teach,0,0,0,,{Augh, I stepped on the eggs!}Đạp lên rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:14.83,Flashback,Homeroom Teach,0,0,0,,{Honestly, why'd they have to be laid \Nin the middle of a classroom?}Thiệt tình, tại sao nó lại ở trong lớp học chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:18.59,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{There go my English answers.}Câu trả lời tiếng anh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:21.98,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I need to protect the math answers \Nat my feet, at least...}Mình phải bảo vệ đáp án toán bằng mọi giá...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:27.09,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Ninpo: Water Escape Technique.}Nhẫn thuật: Thoát nước.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:31.15,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Sensei, I think maybe we \Nshould wrap it up for the...}Em nghĩ hôm nay kết thúc thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:35.10,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Sensei! The floor! Look!}Thầy ơi! Sàn nhà!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.56,Flashback,Homeroom Teach,0,0,0,,{Kumogakure-kun?!}Kumogakure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:39.60,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{He totally just pissed himself!}Dấm đài à trời?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:41.88,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna grab a rag!}Để em đi lấy giẻ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:44.10,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Th-The truth is...}S-Sự thật là...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:47.21,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I've been so nervous since yesterday...}Em đã rất lo lắng...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:51.68,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{And it made me so thirsty, \NI drank a bunch of deep ocean water...}Và nó làm em khát nước nên\N em uống rất nhiều nước biển...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:54.45,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{And now, because of all the salt...}Và giờ... vì lượng muối đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.33,Flashback,Homeroom Teach,0,0,0,,{Ocean water?}Nước biển?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:10:00.20,Flashback,Homeroom Teach,0,0,0,,{And you didn't seem nervous at all before.}Mà tôi thấy em có lo lắng gì đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:02.91,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Here. Sensei, take him to the bathroom.}Đây, thầy dẫn cậu ấy vào nhà vệ sinh đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:06.03,Flashback,Homeroom teach,0,0,0,,{R-Right, I guess I should.}Rồi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:08.77,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Buck up! You're a man, aren't you?}Đừng có khóc! Đàn ông con trai mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:12.44,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Didn't they used to say, \N"Boys, be ambidextrous"?}Người ta hay nói\N "Các chàng trai, phải mạnh mẽ" còn gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:14.45,Flashback,Homeroom teacher,0,0,0,,{Okay, okay...}Rồi rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:16.51,Flashback,Homeroom teacher,0,0,0,,{And it was "be ambitious."}Và câu đúng là "phải tham vọng".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:22.72,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Sensei... I think... after what's happened...}Thầy... em nghĩ... sau chuyện này...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:27.27,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I don't know if I'll be able to handle \Nthe English and math tests...}Em không biết liệu có thể thi\N tiếp toán và tiếng anh không...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:31.23,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{But I did finish the Japanese language portion...}Nhưng em đã hoàn thành quốc ngữ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:35.05,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{So is it okay if I get a bare \Nminimum passing score?}Nên thầy có thể cho em vừa đủ đậu không?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:37.91,Flashback,Homeroom Teach,0,0,0,,{It's fine! Just go to the bathroom and—}Rồi rồi! Đi vào nhà vệ sinh--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:39.87,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I'll take that as an affirmative, then.}Em đã ghi âm lại rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:42.19,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I've got your word.}Em nhớ hết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:44.75,Flashback,Homeroom Teach,0,0,0,,{You scare me, son.}Em... đáng sợ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:48.13,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{What a freak.}Một tên kì lạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.01,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I have to keep coming here?}Từ giờ phải đi học à...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:54.90,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{What a pain.}Phiền phức.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:02.89,Flashback,Mysterious Student,0,0,0,,{I'll be looking forward to seeing you \Nduring the new semester!}Mong chờ được gặp cậu lắm đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:05.85,Flashback,Mysterious Student,0,0,0,,{Kumogakure-kun!}Kumogakure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:09.90,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Who was that?}Ai vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:11.93,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Let's walk partway back together.}Đi về cùng nhau nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:13.52,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Are those...}Và cái đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:15.28,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,Quần lót đã sử dụng.{My "used" underwear.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:16.25,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Wanna buy them?}Mua không?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:18.03,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Why would I?!}Mắc gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:24.24,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Well, wanna come in?}Muốn vào không?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:30.10,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{We had basically no conversation on \Nthe way here, and now you drop that?!}Từ lúc về tới giờ chẳng nói \Ncâu nào xong giờ mời vô nhà?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:31.55,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Welcome home!}Mừng về nhà!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:33.71,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{How was school?}Trường học thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.55,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Is this...}Không lẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:36.87,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{My mother.}Mẹ tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:40.93,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{So young! Ma'am, you're \Nreally young and really cute!}Trẻ quá! Cô trẻ và dễ thương quá vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:46.85,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Uh... so do the two of you live together?}Hai người sống cùng nhau ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.69,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Why do you ask?}Sao lại hỏi thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:52.23,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{It's just... I only saw one futon, so...}Chỉ là... cháu thấy có một cái nệm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:56.19,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{What is this pause supposed to mean?!}Sao tự nhiên lại im lặng?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:12:01.12,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Does it surprise you? \NA young, beautiful mother like me}Ngạc nhiên không? Một bà mẹ trẻ xinh đẹp thế này
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:05.83,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{and her son, at the peak of puberty, \Nsleeping in the same room?}và đứa con trai tuổi dậy thì ngủ chung với nhau?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:09.38,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{No, not really! Families come in all kinds.}K-Không hẳn! Có người này người nọ mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:12.09,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Also, I never said "beautiful."}Với cả cháu không có nói xinh đẹp...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:16.21,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Don't worry. Kuro sleeps on the second floor.}Đừng lo, Kuro ngủ trên tầng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:19.97,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{So, how's the class I'm about to join?}Thế lớp tôi vào học là như nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:21.36,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{What do you mean, "how"?}Như nào là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:24.95,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Like... the number of cliques, their hierarchy...}Kiểu như...bè phái... cấp bậc?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:26.98,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Individual remarkables and deplorables...}Những cá nhân nổi bật và kém nổi bật...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:30.23,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{The landscape of any bullying, \Nany romantic situations...}Bắt nạt? Cặp đôi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:33.71,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Any shoplifters, smokers, \Ndrinkers, fighters...}Trộm cắp? Hút thuốc? Bia rượu? Đánh nhau...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.59,0:12:37.46,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{An outline of any good blackmail material...}Tống tiền này nọ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:40.14,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Also, rumors. Basically anything you know.}Bất cứ thứ gì cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:42.54,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Now, spill, please.}Nào, trả lời đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:45.01,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{What the hell? You are so scary.}Quái gì vậy? Đáng sợ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:50.92,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{I don't know how things are with the guys, \Nbut the girls have four main groups.}Đám con trai thì không rõ \Nnhưng con gái có 4 nhóm chính.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:53.17,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{And where do you fit in?}Cậu nhóm nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:58.47,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Well, before, I was in \Nthe most popular group...}À thì... từng trong nhóm nổi nhất...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:03.18,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{But lately, a bunch of stuff has happened, \Nand I'm kinda floating around.}Nhưng gần đây nhiều chuyện xảy ra nên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:06.50,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Was any part of that funny?}Có gì buồn cười à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:09.26,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Any rumors about the school in general?}Có tin đồn nào trong trường không?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:11.69,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{I'm trying to remember...}Để nhớ đã...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:14.47,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Stuff like, "Someone showed porn \Nto a statue of Ninomiya Kinjiro}Kiểu như "Ai đó chiếu phim sex\N cho tượng Ninomiya Kinjiro
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:17.10,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{and it started looking hunched over."}và nó bắt đầu xem thật" chẳng hạn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.57,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Damn TV won't turn on!}TV không lên!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:24.57,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Oh, the school apparently used \Nto be, like... a military base?}À, có vẻ trường chúng ta ngày\N xưa là căn cứ quân sự.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:27.74,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{And there's a tunnel leading underground \Nin the woods behind the campus.}Và có một đường hầm dẫn vào lòng đất ra khu rừng phía sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:31.03,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Some students who went in there \Non a lark ended up going missing.}Vài học sinh đi vào đó rồi mất tích.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:35.13,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Also, the director is scary.}Và quản lý cũng đáng sợ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.13,0:13:36.59,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,Quản lý?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:39.76,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{He does all kinds of odd \Njobs around the school.}Là người làm mấy việc lặt vặt trong trường.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:42.09,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{A director...}Quản lý...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:44.55,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Hey, it's on!}A lên rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:48.35,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{This show has been so wild lately. \NHate to miss it!}Chương trình này gần đây hay lắm.
