Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:55.67,Flashback,Takachiho,0,0,0,,{It's me, Miss Takachiho!}Là Takachiho đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:56.61,Flashback,Old dudes,0,0,0,,{Where are we?}Đây là đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.11,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Old dudes?}Lão già?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:03.11,Flashback,Old Dude,0,0,0,,{How the fuck do you think we're doing? \NWhere even is this?}Đừng có đùa chứ? Chỗ nào đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:07.25,Flashback,Takachiho,0,0,0,,{Oh, you're the boy who's been \Na shut-in for ten years.}Là đứa tự nhốt mình suốt 10 năm nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:11.71,Flashback,Takachiho,0,0,0,,{But lately, you've been getting violent \Nwith your mother, haven't you?}Nhưng gần đây còn cả bạo lực với mẹ mình nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:17.82,Flashback,Old Dude,0,0,0,,{Do you realize how, while we waste time \Nhere, my anime backlog is growing?!}Bà có biết trong khi đang ở đây thì bao \Nnhiêu anime đang chiếu không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:19.63,Flashback,Old Dude,0,0,0,,{Let me go home already!}Thả tôi ra mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:24.63,Flashback,Takachiho,0,0,0,,{Unfortunately for you, this isn't \Nan intervention or anything.}Không! Cậu không có quyền can thiệp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:28.51,Flashback,Takachiho,0,0,0,,{Although your mother did ask for my help.}Và mẹ cậu đã nhờ bọn tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:31.53,Flashback,Takachiho,0,0,0,,{You've been abusing animals,}Cậu tra tấn động vật,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:35.52,Flashback,Takachiho,0,0,0,,{and lately, you've even been getting \Nviolent with neighborhood kids.}gần đây còn đánh đập trẻ con hàng xóm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:39.02,Flashback,Takachiho,0,0,0,,{So she asked me to deal with you.}Nên bà ấy nhờ ta xử lý cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:43.83,Flashback,Old Dude,0,0,0,,{You wanna "deal" with me?! What the fuck \Nis your wrinkly ass talking about?!}Muốn xử lý thằng này? Bà nói nhảm gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:45.66,Flashback,Old Dude,0,0,0,,{I'm untouchable!}Ta là vô địch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:49.91,Flashback,Old Dude,0,0,0,,{My dad's a government big shot! I can do \Nwhatever I want, and he'll cover it up!}Ông già ta làm trong chính phủ!\N Ta thích làm gì thì ổng cũng sẽ che giấu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:53.05,Flashback,Old Dude,0,0,0,,{Even if I kill you!}Thậm chí cả giết bà!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:03.86,Flashback,Old Dude,0,0,0,,{Ow!}Đau quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:06.45,Flashback,Old Dude,0,0,0,,{Help! Mommy!}Cứu con mẹ ơi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:07.21,Flashback,Old Dudes,0,0,0,,{What the hell?!}Cái quái gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:08.55,Flashback,Old Dudes,0,0,0,,{Is this for real?! Or a prank?!}Là thật hay đùa vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:11.81,Flashback,Takachiho,0,0,0,,{Now then, everyone, let's all quiet down!}Giờ thì tất cả im lặng nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:16.56,Flashback,Takachiho,0,0,0,,{Today, we're going to keep playing \Nuntil there's only one of you left.}Hôm nay chúng ta sẽ chơi đến khi chỉ còn lại 1 người.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:19.08,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Ew, you can see their insides...}Nhìn thấy cả nội tạng kìa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:22.08,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Weird how fast you get used to it, though.}Nhưng mà ngạc nhiên là không thấy gớm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.57,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{I know, right?}Phải chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:28.42,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{If you watch it all the time, \Nit stops being stimulating enough.}Nếu cứ xem hoài sẽ không còn thấy kích thích nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:33.29,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{That's a popular show from the Ninja \NBroadcast Company, }{\i0}{Me and Old Dudes}{\i1}{.}Là chương trình nổi tiếng từ công ty \Ntruyền hình Ninja: Tôi và những lão già.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:40.29,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{They take criminals and accomplices that \Nthe police can't touch from Japan and abroad}Họ bắt lũ tội phạm mà cảnh sát\N không bắt được từ Nhật và nước ngoài
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:42.29,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{and execute them publically.}sau đó xử tử công khai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.24,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Why's it airing on civilian TV?}Tại sao nó lại phát sóng trên kênh cho dân thường?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:54.21,Flashback,Kato,0,0,0,,{Get in.}Vào đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:02.11,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{School, huh?}Trường học à...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:10.46,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Kuro-san... You're serious \Nabout protecting me, right?}Kuro này... anh thực sự bảo vệ tôi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:12.49,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Yeah. Five hundred yen a pop.}Ừ, 500 yên 1 ngày.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:15.89,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{You want me to pay?! \NI thought this was... a friend thing.}Hả? Phải trả tiền thật à? Tưởng ta là bạn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:17.12,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{But this is work.}Đây là công việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:20.10,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{It's... work?}Công việc à...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:22.51,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Hey, it's the shut-in guy!}A, ông anh hikki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:25.08,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Finally going back to school? Have fun!}Cuối cùng cũng đi học à? Cố lên nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.48,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Shut up!}Im đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:29.80,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{You must be pretty cheery \Nabout not getting beaten anymore.}Em cũng nên vui khi hết bị đánh nữa đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.39,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Aw, shut up!}Im đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:36.33,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Whose house is that?}Nhà ai thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:42.36,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{How do you know where I live?}Sao biết tôi sống ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:43.80,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{What do you mean?}Ý cậu là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.99,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Don't you remember how I followed you home \Nwithout you noticing the other day?}Hôm trước tôi theo cậu về nhà mà không biết à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:49.74,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Gross! Don't do that kind of thing!}Gớm quá! Đừng có bám đuôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.24,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Why are we walking to school \Ntogether? Seriously.}Mà tại sao chúng ta lại đi cùng nhau?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.83,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{And Eita-kun's coming back to class, huh?}Và Eita cũng quay lại trường hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:17:00.75,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Y-Yeah. Because Kuro-kun \Nsaid he'd protect me...}Kuro nói sẽ bảo vệ tớ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:04.39,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Well, aren't you two chummy?}Hai người thân thiết ghê nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:07.01,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{We went to the same schools \Nour whole lives, that's all!}Bọn này học cùng cấp 1, 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:12.26,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{He's been bullied by the guys, \Nwhich is, y'know, bad and all...}Tên này toàn bị bắt nạt! Tôi biết bắt nạt là xấu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.86,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{But because he tried to plant \Na camera in the girls' bathroom,}Nhưng cậu ta cứ đặt máy quay\N lén trong nhà vệ sinh nữ,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:17.02,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{none of them will take his side.}nên không ai về phe cậu ta cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:20.21,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{I keep saying, that was all \Na big misunderstanding!}Đã nói là hiểu lầm rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:23.09,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{When I snuck into the girls' bathroom \Nto set up the camera,}Khi tớ chui vào nhà vệ sinh định gắn camera,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:25.60,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{there was already a microphone.}thì đã có gắn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.78,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{And when I told the teacher about it...}Và khi báo cáo lại giáo viên...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:30.77,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{But you did go into the girls' \Nbathroom with a camera.}Thế là cậu cũng có ý định à...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:33.24,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Well...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:37.91,FlashbackItalics,Kuro,0,0,0,,{A microphone. Likely planted \Nby an ally or an enemy.}Máy nghe lén... \NCó thể là đồng minh hoặc kẻ thù...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:40.91,FlashbackItalics,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Better be careful what I say \Non school grounds.}Phải cẩn thận những gì mình nói khi trong trường.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:45.28,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Huh? It's the director.}Ủa? Là quản lý.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:46.94,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{What's he doing here?}Tại sao lại ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:50.85,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{So that's him...}Là hắn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:08.36,FlashbackItalics,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Three hundred twenty-one yen.}321 yên.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:20.51,FlashbackItalics,Kuro,0,0,0,,{He can use clairaudience, huh?}Hắn vừa dùng thấu thị à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,0:18:25.04,Flashback,Teacher,0,0,0,,{Okay, I'm going to introduce \Nthe transfer student now.}Vậy tôi xin giới thiệu học sinh chuyển trường.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:29.17,Flashback,Teacher,0,0,0,,{This is Kumogakure Kuro-kun, \Nwho will be joining us from today on.}Đây là Kumogakure Kuro,\N từ hôm nay sẽ học ở lớp chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.01,0:18:32.49,Flashback,Boy Student,0,0,0,,{He's barefoot?}Chân trần?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:34.05,Flashback,Girl Student,0,0,0,,{He's barefoot...}Chân trần...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:36.98,Flashback,Teacher,0,0,0,,{And then... come on, Eita!}Và... Eita!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:40.08,Flashback,Teacher,0,0,0,,{You're not a transfer student! \NWhat're you standing up for?}Em có phải học sinh chuyển trường đâu? Sao đứng đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:42.81,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Oh, that's, er...}À không...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:47.24,Flashback,Teacher,0,0,0,,{Go on! Both of you, sit down.}Cả hai xuống chỗ ngồi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:56.07,Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,{How about you leave and then \Ncome back in through the rear door?}Sao mày không đi cửa sau vào nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:58.60,Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,{'Cause if you step over my leg, you're dead.}Nếu bước qua chân tao thì đừng trách.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:08.08,Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,{Ow! You little—}Mày! Thằng chó--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:11.35,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Wait, that wasn't me!}Khoan, không phải tớ!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.59,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{My leg just...}Chân tớ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:16.20,Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,{This isn't over, Eita.}Chưa xong đâu Eita.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:19.60,Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,{Did you pull that shit knowing my dad \Nwas an assemblyman for Nerima Ward?}Mày có biết bố tao là nghị sĩ phường Nerima không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:23.29,Flashback,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{I thought he lost the last election, though.}Ủa? Tưởng đợt trước tạch rồi mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:26.60,Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,{Well... I mean, he did, but...}À thì đúng nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:33.43,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Well, this is off to a great start!}Vừa vào đã làm thế là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:34.99,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Do you want me to become a shut-in again?}Muốn tớ thành hikki lắm à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:36.76,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Don't worry about him.}Không cần lo đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:38.62,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Kuro-san!}Kuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:46.46,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Who's that?}Ai thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:48.25,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I'll be back later.}Đi đây một chút.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:21.21,Flashback,Yamada,0,0,0,,{Sorry to ask for your help.}Xin lỗi vì nhờ cậu giúp nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:24.29,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{It's fine! This box is really light!}Không sao, hộp nhẹ mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:27.01,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Well, would you look at this?}Biết phải nói sao đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:29.90,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{I've been in the same class as her \Nfor the past two years,}Mình đã học cùng cô ấy suốt 2 năm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:33.23,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{and Yamada Mitsuki-san \Nhas finally spoken to me.}Và cuối cùng Yamada Mitsuki \Nđã chịu bắt chuyện với mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:36.63,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{She's the prettiest girl in our year, \Nshe's cheerful and sensible,}Cô ấy là xinh đẹp nhất lớp và rất rạng rỡ,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:40.95,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{she treats everybody equally, \Nand she's beloved by guys and girls.}đối xử bình đẳng với mọi \Nngười và ai cũng yêu mến.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:46.35,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{And now I'm walking alone with her \Nin a deserted part of the campus...}Và giờ mình đi chung vói cô ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:48.06,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,Không có lẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:54.80,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Can you think of an affectionate way someone \Nmight refer to a sweet-natured adult cat?}Cậu có thể tìm cách miêu tả một\N chú mèo trưởng thành ngọt ngào không?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:57.83,Flashback,Yamada,0,0,0,,{Um... A pussycat?}Ngạo mạn?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.68,0:21:01.45,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{I might even end up losing my virgnity!}Mình sẽ bị mất trinh bởi cô ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:03.26,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{I need to prepare mentally!}Phải chuẩn bị tinh thần.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:05.08,Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,{Hey, it's Eita!}Này Eita!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:07.36,Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,{Fancy running into you back here.}Mày đến đây làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:10.83,Flashback,Yamada,0,0,0,,{You asked me to bring him, Azuma-kun.}Cậu nhờ tớ gọi cậu ấy mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:11.75,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Yamada-san?!}Yamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:15.79,Flashback,Yamada,0,0,0,,{Good luck, Eita-kun!}Cố lên nhé Eita!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.14,Flashback,Yamada,0,0,0,,Gặp sau!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:22.70,Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,{I actually had some questions for you.}Tao có chuyện muốn hỏi mày đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:24.60,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{U-Uh...}Hả...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:32.50,Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,{I'm trying to talk here.}Tao đang hỏi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:35.36,Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,{Lately I've been seeing}Gần đây tao có thấy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:39.36,Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,{a bunch of nasty anonymous postings \Non social media, targeted at yours truly.}một loạt các bài đăng khó chịu nhắm vào tao đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:42.94,Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,{You know anything about that?}Mày không biết à?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:44.85,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{N-No...}K-Không...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:49.37,Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,{No? 'Cause when I looked it up, \Nsome of these posts...}Hả? Nhưng khi tao tìm hiểu mấy bài đăng đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:53.37,Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,{were from a day when we had class. \NA pop quiz, in fact.}thì đều được đăng vào ngày kiểm tra.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:56.87,Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,{So it couldn't be anyone from our class.}Nên chắc chắn không ai trong lớp ta có thể làm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:22:01.13,Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,{With the exception of you, Eita-kun, \Nwho didn't come in that day.}Ngoại trừ một kẻ không tham gia hôm đó, là mày.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:04.14,Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,{You were talking all that shit \Nabout me, weren't you?}Mày dám nói những cái đó về tao à?
